casebody.data:
No. 11,

Original.

Ex parte: In the Matter of The Cudahy Packing Company, Petitioner. Argued November 28, 1910. Decided December 5, 1910. Mr. Ralph W. Breckenridge and Mr. Charles J. Greene for petitioner.

Petition for a writ of mandamus denied, rule discharged, and petition dismissed, on the authority of In re Pennsylvania Company, Petitioner &c., 137 U. S. 451.

*669Mr. Constantine J. Smyth and Mr. Edward P. Smith for respondent.
